body: There is no happy ending in netorare . Even if the guy ends up with the girl somehow she is already fucked by a number of guys and in some cases by animals.
Would be good if Kyoden plots once in a while have a happy end, like tsuyatsuya works. The doubt would be good for the readers.
All this time I thought this series was a rare Sanbun Kyoden happy ending... nope. :(
